1. Поля User:
    -id, firstname, lastname, age, email, password, role
2. В таблице отображаются все кроме пароля.
3. МО add: first name, last name, age, email, pass, role
4. МО edit: id(disabled), first name, last name, age, email, pass, role
5. МО del: id, first name, last name, age, email, role
6. Admin panel id, first name, last name, age, email, role, edit_btn, delete_btn
7. User page id, first name, last name, age, email, role
